tes C2472.  \n  \n```  \n// C2472.cpp  \n// compile with: /clr:pure  \n// C2472 expected  \n  \n#include <cstdlib>  \n  \nint main()  \n{  \n   int * __ptr32 p32;  \n   int * __ptr64 p64;  \n  \n   p32 = (int * __ptr32)malloc(4);  \n   p64 = p32;  \n}  \n```  \n  \n## See Also  \n [/clr (Common Language Runtime Compilation)](../../build/reference/clr-common-language-runtime-compilation.md)"}